divs: sighting detailsi was taking nature photos. i snapped several pictures of a small pond on route 40. was located between the towns of clark center and martinsville, illinois in clark county, between noon-1:00 p.m. i saw nothing whatsoever with the naked eye. when i uploaded the pictures onto the computer, i saw an object above the pond, above the treeline. cigar shaped, gold\copper colored, with black as well. it was not a bird, as i've taken many pictures of birds in flight with my olympus camera. at no time did i ever see the object with the naked eye, nor did i hear a noise.
Summary: Object appeared in photograph. Not visible to naked eye.
